  "description": "Figure-eight at tangle 0.8 with feedback at 0.93 — the loop is twisted and the resonance cannot escape it. Square LFO hard-gates the filter while the delay base is swept by LFO2. The symmetric matrix means chaos is mirrored: left and right are equally unstable. A controlled tornado.",
